    <title>Amend Misinterpreted Excessive Regulation In Corporate America Act</title>
    <titles>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To reduce the unintended costs and burdens that the Sarbanes-Oxley Act of 2002 imposes on United States businesses, while maintaining that Act's goals of bolstering confidence in the integrity of publicly held companies.</title>
